```{r ampulla 32706533, include=FALSE}

PMID_32706533 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32706533', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32706533 <- paste0(PMID_32706533$journal,' ', PMID_32706533$year, ' ', PMID_32706533$month,';', PMID_32706533$volume,'(', PMID_32706533$number,'):', PMID_32706533$pages)

PubMed_32706533 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32706533$eprint)

doi_32706533 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32706533$doi)

Sys.sleep(2)
```
